title.dwm.sonic_device.mode.scan.descrip: Allows you to get information about a block or entity.
title.dwm.sonic_device.mode.setting.desc:
Allows you to change the state of various blocks/mechanisms, as well as interact in a special way with some entities. 

§6WARNING§r: Does not work with wood or some hair dryers!
title.dwm.sonic_device.mode.tardis_reloc: Allows you to set a new destination location for the TARDIS. Before use, you must bind the device to the TARDIS.
